COMMENT ON COLUMN invariant_checks.filter_expression IS 'Condition selecting the universe of rows this invariant applies to. Empty means all rows.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN invariant_checks.assertion_expression IS 'The per-row condition that must be TRUE for every row in scope.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN invariant_checks.sql_filter IS 'Optional SQL WHERE clause that selects the universe of rows in scope for this invariant (e.g. distortion_type = ''D''). Empty string means all rows.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN invariant_checks.sql_assertion IS 'The SQL WHERE clause (without WHERE keyword) that counts PASSING rows from vw_treatment_rankings for this invariant. Used by run_invariant_checks() to evaluate each assertion dynamically from the rulebook table.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN invariant_checks.pass_count IS 'Rows where the invariant holds. Populated by 05b-customize-data.sql from a live query against vw_treatment_rankings.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN invariant_checks.fail_count IS 'Rows where the invariant is violated. Any FailCount > 0 is a build-breaking bug.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN invariant_checks.severity IS 'critical | warning — critical means any FailCount > 0 is a build-breaking bug.';

